column5: Awesome first Muskie! Welcome to OFC!
I give that a 10 on the !DANG! scale. Very impressive for a first fish. Congrats to you! What did you catch it on?
Great fish. getting your first Geo Bay musky can be hard as when they are on they are on but most of the times there off! Congrats
missed another big fella tonight got it up to 10 feet from the boat and lost it ,nothing worse then NOT seeing it ,thanks for all the complements so far appreciate it
beauty fish man!!!!! hope you know you will now spends hundreds anualy on baits, rods and tackle  keep casting! ( and don't forget to figure 8)!
Very nice first Muskie,, what did ya catcher on ? Welcome aboard!!
That's helluva first fish!
perch turbo jack

Well........your goose is cooked now!! You'll be a rabid muskie chaser til you are finally afflicted with chronic rheumatoid castitis, and can no longer reel and cannot close your hands.  Very nice fish......what did it hit on?
NICE FISH !!!!!!! congrats on your big ski.  ...cheers
just started this crazy obsession with skies a month ago ,got my first one tonight,she revived nicely ,my dads in the pic
Wow - nice fish.  Looks like your dad is doing some weight lifting with that huge muskie!
Nice Fish and welcome to the board!
thanks fellas been lurking around decided to join up
Awesome fish! Welcome to OFC.
Welcome to the board and a real NICE Musky
great fish and welcome to the board
Nice fish!   What a way to start!!!  Welcome!
Congrats on that! A great first muskie ... it would appear you set the bar pretty high right away.  Congrats again ...  Pete
All these Ski's are making me real anxious to catch my first one! Hopefully in October at Stony Lake.
wow great catch! that is huge!
Welcome to the board, that sure is a nice fish!  Maureen
Welcome! a very nice fish! LOL a good way to start! Some nice ones in the GB, and plenty of water to look for them.
That is a dang nice 'first' fish .... congrats in a big way.
Congrats on the large one beauty first fish
Wow...you sure opened my eyes!  Great way to intro yourself.  Welcome to the board and good luck out there!
NICE FISH!!!!!!!!!!!!
nice looking fish. Welcome.
Ok you've now wnet and did it, you're now inflected with muskietis. Repet after me " Hi my name is ...........
Wow, congrats on your 'ski. Welcome to OFC.  I believe it is E. Masquinongyitis that Dr. Trophymuskie had diagnosed you with. LOL
wow, heck of a first fish, and from GBay to boot.  nicely done
Wow, that is one heck of a first muskie!  Congrats on a GB hawg... guess you have the official muskie bug now  Good fishing!  Aaron
Welcome aboard! That is one heck of a fish...congrats to you.
Does "muskieitis" have a 10-step program for recovery  Well done and welcome to the board - hope your second fish posting is as big as the first!
Congrats man, beauty fish
